HEADWORD: Tennysonian
<hw>Ten`ny*so"ni*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to <person>Alfred (Lord) Tennyson</person>, the English poet
(1809-92); resembling, or having some of the characteristics of, his
poetry, as simplicity, pictorial quality, sensuousness, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
